headline: Did Rockwell’s Saudi EV Factory Deal Just Reframe Rockwell Automation's (ROK) Industrial Software Ambitions?
summary: Rockwell Automation announced an expanded collaboration with Lucid to deploy its FactoryTalk MES and training programs at Saudi Arabia’s first vehicle manufacturing facility in King Abdullah Economic City, enhancing real-time visibility and control across all major production shops. By pairing advanced manufacturing software with local workforce training, the partnership aligns Rockwell’s industrial automation capabilities with Saudi Arabia’s Vision 2030 push to build an electric vehicle...

headline: Rockwell Automation to Present at Barclays 43rd Annual Industrial Select Conference
summary: MILWAUKEE, January 30, 2026--Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK) Chairman and CEO, Blake Moret, and SVP, Software and Control, Matheus Bulho, will present at Barclays 43rd Annual Industrial Select Conference on Wednesday, Feb. 18, 2026, in Miami Beach, Fla.
